EVT_8014205_NAME;Death of Stalin;;;;;;;;;;X;;;;;;;
EVT_8014205_DESC;Stalin's health deteriorated towards the end of World War II. He suffered from atherosclerosis from his heavy smoking. He suffered a mild stroke around the time of the Victory parade, and a severe heart attack in October 1945.;;;;;;;;;;X;;;;;;;
